            <h1>Signs of Loneliness</h1>
            <p>It is difficult for you to have a good sleep. </p>
            <p>You are not able to sacrifice the time you spend on social media.</p>
            <p>You eat eating a lot or you have not eaten a proper meal since a long time.</p>
            <p>You have broken the record of binge watching movies or a series of you favourite episodes. </p>
            <p3>You feel alienated or alone when you are around people, be it at your workplace or even on any public transport.</p3>
