            <h1>Little Tips</h1>
            <p>Keeping your mind busy will divert your feelings of loneliness and isolation.</p>
            <p>You Can Try : </p>
            <p>Practice yoga and meditation.</p>
            <p>Be around animals. Adopt a pet to keep you company.</p>
            <p>Find activities where you surround yourself with people.</p>
            <p>Design a routine for yourself including the things you enjoy.</p>
            <p>Spend time for yourself and not focus on knowing the lives of the people in your phone.</p>
            <p3>Try helping the community as you get to interact with people and help someone as well.</p3>
